data.title: Investing in Kazakhstan - Opportunities in Aktobe Region
data.meta_description: Investing in Kazakhstan - Opportunities in Aktobe Region - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: The document describes 10 investment projects in mining, manufacturing and oil industries located in the Aktobe region of Kazakhstan. The projects involve production of steel, iron ore concentrate, nickel-cobalt concentrate, ferronickel, copper cathode, titanium-zirconium ores, chrome ore, enriched kaolin and involve building new facilities or expanding existing ones. Total investments in the projects range from $30 million to $1.2 billion and they will create new production facilities and jobs in the Aktobe region of Kazakhstan.
